"{\"uid\": \"si.com-fannation-boxing-petecio-s-triumph-and-lopez-s-close-call-day-9-at-the-paris-olympics-01j4hs7k6nzd\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Mohamed Bahaa  For the second consecutive Olympics, Nesthy Petecio has secured a medal, solidifying her status as one of the most prominent figures in Philippine sports history.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 55, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesthy_Petecio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nesthy Petecio\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesthy_Petecio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesthy_Petecio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Day 9 of the 2024 Paris Olympics, the 32-year-old boxing sensation from Davao City made history by becoming the first Filipino boxer to win two Olympic medals.\", \"from\": 181, \"to\": 343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Davao City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davao_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petecio achieved this feat by defeating China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Xu Zichun with a unanimous 5-0 victory in the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 57kg quarterfinals.\", \"from\": 344, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having claimed a silver medal at the Tokyo Games, Petecio now sets her sights on gold.\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is scheduled to face Poland's rising star Julia Szeremeta in the semifinals on Wednesday, August 7.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 661, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 583, \"end\": 589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"score\": 0.999999993684014, \"rank\": 3.266638729741431e-09, \"text\": \"Poland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Poland\"}, {\"begin\": 604, \"end\": 609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999995764170295, \"rank\": 4.233128521442573e-07, \"text\": \"Julia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Szeremeta, 20, earned her semifinal spot with a decisive 5-0 win over Ashleyann Lozada Motta of Puerto Rico.\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Motta_di_Livenza\", \"score\": 0.9992896646942034, \"rank\": 0.0007095611642446535, \"text\": \"Motta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Motta_di_Livenza\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Motta_di_Livenza\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9999970802593331, \"rank\": 2.9194284993408745e-06, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petecio displayed remarkable skill and strategy against the taller Xu, using her agility and experience to land powerful overhand lefts repeatedly.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She dominated the first round, sweeping all five judges' scorecards.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Xu attempted to press the attack with aggressive moves, Petecio capitalized on her opponent's overreaching by countering with precise right hooks and deftly dodging incoming punches.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite trailing 20-18 on all cards after two rounds, Xu mounted a fierce offensive in the third, launching combinations to Petecio\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s body and even forcing her to the floor in the opening moments.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Petecio maintained her composure, trading blows with Xu and landing strategic left hands to fend off her opponent's relentless assault.\", \"from\": 1375, \"to\": 1519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As Petecio continues her journey in the semifinals, another Filipino boxer, Aira Villegas, also has her eyes on the medal podium.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1581, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 0.9941486194078957, \"rank\": 0.005736132200826854, \"text\": \"Filipino\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 1597, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aira\", \"score\": 0.9999987124564644, \"rank\": 7.103697671931211e-07, \"text\": \"Aira\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aira\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Competing in the 50kg category, Villegas will go up against Turkey\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Buse Naz \\u00c3\\u0087ak\\u00c4\\u00b1ro\\u00c4\\u009flu in her own semifinal match on Thursday.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a contrasting outcome, Cuban boxing legend Arlen Lopez finds himself returning home with a bronze medal instead of gold.\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1811, \"end\": 1816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"score\": 0.8578759510606176, \"rank\": 0.16566393003427057, \"text\": \"Cuban\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba\"}, {\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arlen_L\\u00f3pez\", \"score\": 0.9999998984553764, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arlen Lopez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arlen_L\\u00f3pez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arlen_L\\u00f3pez\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old experienced a narrow 3-2 defeat against Ukraine\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Oleksandr Khyzhniak in the men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 80kg semifinals, ending his pursuit of becoming the third boxer in history to win three Olympic gold medals.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1977, \"end\": 1996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Khyzhniak\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Oleksandr Khyzhniak\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Khyzhniak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Oleksandr_Khyzhniak\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khyzhniak, a silver medalist from the Tokyo Games, showcased his signature aggressive style, relentlessly attacking Lopez with combinations throughout the match.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lopez attempted to respond with powerful single punches but struggled to keep up with Khyzhniak\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s pace, abandoning his usual strategic approach.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the decisive third round, Lopez showed signs of fatigue as Khyzhniak continued his onslaught, dominating the exchanges.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The match concluded with a heated exchange between the two fighters, as Khyzhniak landed a punch after the final bell, causing a tense stare-down between the two.\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2717, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In another development, Cuba\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Erislandy Alvarez is set to compete for gold in the 63.5kg category after securing a 5-0 victory against Georgia\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Lasha Guruli.\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2869, \"end\": 2881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lasha_Guruli\", \"score\": 0.9999999596211645, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lasha Guruli\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lasha_Guruli\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lasha_Guruli\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alvarez will face France\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Sofiane Oumiha, a three-time world champion, who advanced with a 4-1 decision over Canada\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Wyatt Sanford.\", \"from\": 2883, \"to\": 3020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2912, \"end\": 2926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sofiane_Oumiha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sofiane Oumiha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sofiane_Oumiha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sofiane_Oumiha\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Full Results:  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Lin Yu Ting (TPE) 5-0 Svetlana Kamenova Staneva (BUL)  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Esra Yildiz Kahraman (TUR) 4-1 Jucielen Cerqueira Romeu (BRA)  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Nesthy Petecio (PHI) 5-0 Xu Zichun (CHN)  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Julia Szeremeta (POL) 5-0 Ashleyann Lozada Motta (PUR)  \\u00c2\\u00b7\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2Women's 75kg \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 Quarterfinals:  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Li Qian (CHN) 4-1 Lovlina Borgohain (IND)  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Caitlin Parker (AUS) 4-1 Khadija Mardi (MAR)  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Cindy Winner Djankeu Ngamba (EOR) 5-0 Davina Michel (FRA)  o\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0 Atheyna Bibeichi Bylon (PAN) 3-2 Elzbieta Wojcik (POL)  \\u00c2\\u00b7\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00c2W